The Bank.description: Near the top of the gold pile on top of the bank.

The Mayor's House.description: Behind the flames in the fireplace.

Windmill 1.description: On the 3rd floor of the Windmill.

Windmill 2.description: On the sail of the Windmill.

Chimney.description: Next to the front chimney on top of the barn.

West Mountains.description: Inside the water coming from the west mountain.

The Root.description: At the lowest point of root at the south of the island.

The Pit.description: At the bottom of the obsidian and coal pit.

Gravel Quarry 1.description: Above the stairs in the gravel quarry.

Gravel Quarry 2.description: On the first level down of wooden slabs in the corner in the gravel quarry.

Bones 1.description: On top of the rib bones near the southwest edge of the island.

Bones 2.description: Inside a hidden room in the bones. Jump into a hole located at [-286, 94, -179], or jump onto the bone platform at [-276, 93, -180].

Bones 3.description: Under a quartz stair in the skull.

Bones 4.description: On top of the rib bones near the northeast edge of the island.

The Floating Bush.description: Walk over the barrier blocks at [-390, 84, -228]. The fairy soul is in the leaves floating over the void.

North Edge.description: Off the north edge of the island.

Skeleton Cave.description: Inside of the cave on the north edge of the island.

Edge Stairs.description: On the right of a set of stairs leading off the edge of the island. Walk over the green wool.

Northern Mountain.description: On top of the northernmost mountain.

Bridge 1.description: On the right of the bridge.

Bridge 2.description: On the left of the bridge.

East Edge 1.description: The easternmost edge of the island.

East Edge 2.description: On barrier blocks east of the island.

West Edge.description: At the westernmost edge of the island.

North Edge 1.description: On the north edge of the island.

North Edge 2.description: At the northernmost edge of the island.

The Tallest Roof.description: On top of the highest doubled roof.

Top of the Mountain.description: At the top of the mountain.

In the Flames.description: Behind the flames of the middle hopper on the wall.

Edge of the Roof.description: On the edge of the leftmost tower.

Stairs.description: Under the left of the staircase.

Lava Pool.description: Under the lower block in the pool.

The Lever Hole.description: Flip the lever at [-307, 113, -675] and go down the hole to the left.
